byline.contributor: Sewell Chan reported from London, and Christina Anderson from Stockholm.
byline.original: By SEWELL CHAN and CHRISTINA ANDERSON

headline.main: Assange Is Questioned in London Over Rape Accusation in Sweden

snippet: The WikiLeaks founder was interviewed by prosecutors in the 2010 case for the first time. He has been living in the Ecuadorean Embassy in Britain since 2012....
lead_paragraph: The WikiLeaks founder was interviewed by prosecutors in the 2010 case for the first time. He has been living in the Ecuadorean Embassy in Britain since 2012.
